### ðŸ“ˆ Visual Highlights

| Section        | Visual Type         | Description |
|----------------|---------------------|-------------|
| KPIs           | Card                | Tweet Count, Positive %, Avg Length, Avg Retweets |
| Trend Analysis | Line Chart          | Sentiment over time using CalendarTable |
| Sentiment Split| Donut Chart         | Overall sentiment distribution |
| Airline-wise   | Stacked Bar Chart   | Sentiment by Airline |
| Text Insights  | Word Cloud          | Most used words per sentiment (Advanced Visual) |
| Deep Dive      | Table/Matrix        | Full tweet details with sentiment |
| Interactions   | Slicers             | Filters for Airline, Sentiment, Date |

