## ðŸ§  DAX Measures (Examples)

```dax
Positive Count = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(Twitter_Sentiment_Analyzed), Twitter_Sentiment_Analyzed[Polarity_Sentiment] = "positive")

% Positive = DIVIDE([Positive Count], [Total Tweets], 0)

Avg Tweet Length = AVERAGEX(Twitter_Sentiment_Analyzed, LEN(Twitter_Sentiment_Analyzed[Clean_Tweet]))

Avg Retweets = AVERAGE(Twitter_Sentiment_Analyzed[Retweets])

